table_caption: Significant positive findings over 1000 runs. T0,Tl,Tldq are density regressions with the identity, logarithm, and log density‐quantile transformation described in Section 2.3. Bonferroni, FDR (Benjamini & Hochberg, 1995) refer to edgewise regression with different multiplicity correction procedures. PC refers to the principal component regression with the top 10 components, the number chosen by minimizing the sum of type I error (significance ratio in non‐localized situation) and type II error (none significance ratio in localized situation).
